    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>关注</strong>并将我们的系列怪奇小说与宇宙恐怖故事<strong>加入愿望单</strong>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/29f75b0b52c56f363d6891483eb8a4ae.avif?t=1729167634\" width=230 height=86 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/16d8c6ea27ae6a98e8b23a4ebd76df8a.avif?t=1729167634\" width=230 height=86 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/fac9db1af8ad4e093fc6eeb07176f7e1.webp?t=1729167634\" width=620 height=16 /></span><strong>!!!  所有收入将捐赠给乌克兰战争中的灾民  !!!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >^ 点击查看详情</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/fac9db1af8ad4e093fc6eeb07176f7e1.webp?t=1729167634\" width=620 height=16 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是否好奇过，创造出怪诞小说与星辰噩梦的大师会有着什么样的<strong>梦境</strong>？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在你将有机会见证<strong>H·P·洛夫克拉夫特的噩梦</strong>，这个可怕的世界起源于他在1927年所写的信件，收件人是享誉盛名的阿卡姆之屋出版社联合创始人唐纳德·旺德里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >赶快备好车票，找一个舒服的位置做好，<strong>列车员</strong>随后便到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/c5254a6c39736f06b46ab2f7dc04c00d.avif?t=1729167634\" width=620 height=151 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入<strong>洛夫克拉夫特的梦境</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在闲暇时光中踏上一段不可思议的旅程（游戏长度不超过<strong>10分钟</strong>）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>了解</strong>有关作者的趣闻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >见证洛夫克拉夫特本人的噩梦，畅享<strong>拥有完整配音的3D游戏</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原作的电子书与有声读物版本（包含多种格式与语言），官方壁纸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《远古的民族》</strong>短篇小说电子书版本（仅有英文版）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2291520/extras/c211b2a700fc14c07bcb0b2adf7a3539.avif?t=1729167634\" width=216 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >访问文件方法：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的Steam库中右击<strong>Dagon</strong> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择<i><strong>管理&gt;</strong></i> </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击<i><strong>浏览本地文件</strong></i></p></li></ul>",
